        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer593853734" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9148657274906984725">Patrick O’Scheen pulls it off in Dreamer, using excellent word-imagery to make the world of dragons and morgiths and magic and sorcery surprisingly believable. He takes the reader on a journey that crisscrosses kingdoms and relationships with a mostly likeable cast of unlikely friends. Simultaneously, he tells two stories etched in two different time periods, using two of the same characters. Unique and enjoyable.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


